{"tid":403024,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺係香港講普通話既人無資格大聲講嘢","createTime":"2017-09-17T00:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T08:08:28.000Z","uid":117390,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9858a04ccdcb327c887497153feac0e838b421c","tid":403024,"uid":117390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:45:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老味<br />\n有時去啲地方要開門入 / 入升降機果陣，<br />\n一開門就會讓人地先出，<br />\n咁樣禮讓無問題丫，<br />\n但係如果聽到出黎果個或果幾個人係度大聲講普通話，<br />\n我真係慶，好撚討厭，<br />\n尤其是大陸師奶，包括嫁落黎香港果啲，有乜資格大聲用普通話講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a26d1bb74123d8cc0147a9180bc260473d6a425","tid":403024,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:49:06.000Z","msg":"好快到講廣東話既冇資格"},{"pid":"8a2f20dbd75d227498dc4e0ef7a098070fa07a06","tid":403024,"uid":117390,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T01:05:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好快到講廣東話既冇資格</blockquote><br />\n而家啲小學中學生真係恐怖，好多都成堆唔知講緊乜話，舊時我讀小學果陣，普通話唔撚合格先係正路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5bdff3e7bf061dac8db384a35b95f90d6cad15","tid":403024,"uid":71303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T01:39:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">操你媽的</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">特大</span>"},{"pid":"af9c19d5438cacbcccc99e77ddc0052c81b6676d","tid":403024,"uid":113921,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T01:46:11.000Z","msg":"普通話係國家法定語言，而根據基本法第一條<span style=\"color: red;\"> 香港特別行政區是中華人民共和國不可分離的部分</span>。<br />\n因此係香港講普通話，絕對係合情合理合法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70d7b42d41be861d1cc1135a421f4fff377a1ec","tid":403024,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T01:50:37.000Z","msg":"支那人入電梯會唔理你撞埋嚟,我一腳踢開佢個喼"},{"pid":"21d00aaf2002d8b4313523237a210562d2fb39f5","tid":403024,"uid":128102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T01:52:26.000Z","msg":"岩啊<br />\n<br />\n依家講普通話班人好似當自己大撚晒咁 <br />\n有時落街聽到d細路用普通話傾計真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家廣州d細路已經唔識/唔肯講廣東話<br />\n巴打一定要捍衛廣東話係香港傳承落去"},{"pid":"805f77d94fe80c2fe3365b5ad9974aa6aebd3588","tid":403024,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T01:55:01.000Z","msg":"聽到講普通話<br />\n迎面黎就撞佢膊<br />\n<br />\n係前面就踩佢鞋爭"},{"pid":"d4c2100c0c6c26812cf44c13b1aab97e1b846109","tid":403024,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T01:56:59.000Z","msg":"試過有人用普通話問我路，我用英文問佢係咪台灣人，佢答我來自上海，我即刻用廣東話屌佢老母再轉身走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d0b91687ba87b675c92da4d32bd8addd7e6dc2","tid":403024,"uid":146595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:13:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得其實可以"},{"pid":"60411e71f19d7353b1c9abfb7be59b4ba21ad242","tid":403024,"uid":143727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過有人用普通話問我路，我用英文問佢係咪台灣人，佢答我來自上海，我即刻用廣東話屌佢老母再轉身走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果佢答你「我是台灣人」，咁你會點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6786ddcc69bc418f288a70b31f4bc9a155eaf7","tid":403024,"uid":143727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:17:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽到講普通話<br />\n迎面黎就撞佢膊<br />\n<br />\n係前面就踩佢鞋爭</blockquote><br />\n「講」就兇狠，「做」就碌撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b0bb324829cf6d5edc524903a561eb87d30af6","tid":403024,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽到講普通話<br />\n迎面黎就撞佢膊<br />\n<br />\n係前面就踩佢鞋爭</blockquote><br />\n「講」就兇狠，「做」就碌撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />